This '''spy ship''' was a scout vessel employed by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Cavik Toth]]'s [[Sabaoth Squadron/Legends|Sabaoth Squadron]] around the time of the [[Occupation of Karthakk]]. Its design resembled the U-shape of a [[Sabaoth Frigate]], but was the size of a starfighter and unarmed.

[[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Adi Gallia/Legends|Adi Gallia]] encountered a spy ship during a meeting with [[Reti]] in the [[Ruby Nebula]], moments after a [[C-9979 landing craft/Legends|C-9979 landing craft]] arrived in the vicinity. Registering as an unknown craft, the spy ship was presumably tapping into communications between Gallia and Reti. The Jedi Master destroyed the spy ship from her [[Delta-7 Aethersprite-class light interceptor/Legends|Delta-7 ''Aethersprite''-class light interceptor]], though she would later come into conflict with the entire Sabaoth Squadron.

==Behind the scenes==
The destruction of the spy ship constitutes the hidden objective in the first mission (The Informant) of ''Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter''.

